    • Method Detail

      • tptpParse

        public int tptpParse()
        This method translates the entire KB to TPTP format, storing the translation for each Formula in the List identified by the private member Formula.theTptpFormulas. Use Formula.getTheTptpFormulas() to accesss the TPTP sentences (Strings) that constitute the translation for a single SUO-KIF Formula.
        Returns:
        An int indicating the number of Formulas that were successfully translated.
